   Tulu, Dereje; Temteme, Shiferaw; Aleme, Melkam, Ethiopian Inst Agr Res, Tepi Agr Res Ctr, Tepi, Ethiopia.
   Bogale, Ararsa, Ethiopian Inst Agr Res, Holeta Agr Res Ctr, Holeta, Ethiopia.
